"{\"uid\": \"geosuper.tv-latest-36158-neeraj-chopra-wins-another-gold-before-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"India's world-renowned javelin thrower Neeraj Chopra bagged gold medal in his first competition at home in three years on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 39, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Chopra was not impressed with his below-par 82.27 metre throw as he gears up to defend his titles at the Paris Olympics this year.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chopra immediately returned home to take part in the Federation Cup in Bhubaneswar after he kick started his season with a second-place finish at the Diamond League meeting in Doha on Friday  Chopra clinched the medal with his fourth attempt and did not take the final two throws.\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 555, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9685291287975428, \"rank\": 0.03247370427261089, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9994418031037755, \"rank\": 0.0005585086539555238, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came here after competing in Doha and there was not much recovery time,\\\" Chopra told reporters on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9994418031037755, \"rank\": 0.0005585086539555238, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I competed in this kind of weather after a while.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not feeling that good ... so I decided to stop after four throws.\\\"\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us not talk about the throw, it was not up to the mark.\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This one is not my consistent type of throw.\\\"\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 901, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chopra also said that the 90-metre throw will come at the right place and at the right time, bearing in mind his personal best of 89.94 metres.\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It felt great to compete in India after a long time with so many people turning up to support me,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8728739061014884, \"rank\": 0.14508269176554434, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Choprawill take part in events in the Czech Republic and Finland before Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"score\": 0.638350211871372, \"rank\": 0.5660190478636704, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9331041745752137, \"rank\": 0.05195236051439471, \"text\": \"Finland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's going to be really tough competition in Paris,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1294, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999983216752513, \"rank\": 1.6783276168789965e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Doha too, the competition was intense.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9994418031037755, \"rank\": 0.0005585086539555238, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a couple of more events before the Olympics, and will try to throw better.\\\"\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GEO SUPER, All Rights Reserved\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}]}"